headline.print_headline: Ocean Crash Kills Teen Pilot Seeking World Record
headline.main: Ocean Crash Kills Teen Pilot Seeking World Record

lead_paragraph: His pilot's license fresh in his hands, an Indiana teenager set out in June for the adventure of a lifetime: an around-the-world flight with his father designed to break a record and raise money to build schools in his father's native Pakistan.
